Func :©factorstep(Int): step-by-step factor :Local m,k,lfail1,lfail2,lfail3,matdiv,s,msg :s:=check_type_arg(n,"POSINT",0) :If s≠"ok" Then : Return s :ElseIf n=1 Then : n :ElseIf is_small_prime(n,true) Then : n :Else :matdiv:=[[0]] :lfail1:=0 :lfail2:=0 :lfail3:=0 :m:=n :k:=2 :While m≠1 and k^2≤m :©we suppose that the list of prime numbers <20 are known : If is_small_prime(m,true) Then : k:=m : matdiv:=factor_sp(matdiv,[[m,m]]) : m:=1 : Exit : EndIf : If mod(m,k)=0 Then : If lfail1≠0 and lfail2=0 : displist({lfail1,lib_msg("not_divisor",false),m}) : If lfail1≠0 and lfail2≠0 and lfail3=0 : displist({lfail1,"and",lfail2,lib_msg("not_divisors",false),m}) : If lfail1≠0 and lfail2≠0 and lfail3≠0 : displist({lfail1,", ",lfail2,"...",lfail3,lib_msg("not_divisors",false),m}) : lfail1:=0 : lfail2:=0 : lfail3:=0 : msg:=" " : If k=2 and k>10 Then : msg:=lib_msg("last_even",false) : ElseIf k=3 Then : msg:=lib_msg("sum3",false) : ElseIf mod(k,10)=5 Then : msg:=lib_msg("last5",false) : ElseIf mod(k,10)=0 Then : msg:=lib_msg("last0",false) : EndIf : displist({k,lib_msg("divisor",false),m,msg}) : displist({m,"/",k,"=",m/k}) : matdiv:=factor_sp(matdiv,[[m,k]]) : m:=m/k : Else : If lfail1=0 Then : lfail1:=k : ElseIf lfail2=0 Then : lfail2:=k : Else : lfail3:=k : EndIf : k:=nextprime(k+1) : EndIf : If k^2>m Then : If lfail1≠0 and lfail2=0 : displist({lfail1,lib_msg("not_divisor",false),m}) : If lfail1≠0 and lfail2≠0 and lfail3=0 : displist({lfail1,"and",lfail2,lib_msg("not_divisors",false),m}) : If lfail1≠0 and lfail2≠0 and lfail3≠0 : displist({lfail1,", ",lfail2,"...",lfail3,lib_msg("not_divisors",false),m}) : If k≠m:Disp factor(k^2),">",m : displist({m,lib_msg("is_prime",false)}) : EndIf :EndWhile :If m≠1 :matdiv:=factor_sp(matdiv,[[m,m]]) :©matdiv:=factor_sp(matdiv,[1,1]) :Disp matdiv :Disp n,"=",factor(n) :n :EndIf :EndFunc

Func :©primecount(a,b): #primes between a & b :Local k,prcount,s,a,b :a:=n1:b:=n2 :s:=check_type_arg(n1,"POSINT",1) :If s≠"ok" Then : Return s :EndIf :s:=check_type_arg(n2,"POSINT",2) :If s≠"ok" Then : Return s :EndIf :a:=min(n1,n2) :b:=max(n1,n2) :prcount:=when(a≤2≤b,1,0) :If mod(a,2)=0:a:=a+1 :For k,a,b,2 :If isPrime(k):prcount:=prcount+1 :EndFor :Return prcount :EndFunc
